                "invention-title": [
                    "Nuclear power generation and heat supply coupled hydrogen-rich blast furnace-converter comprehensive circulation system",
                    "一种核能发电、供热耦合富氢高炉-转炉的综合循环系统"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a nuclear energy power generation and heat supply coupled hydrogen-rich blast furnace-converter comprehensive circulation system. The system comprises a nuclear energy power generation system, a nuclear energy hydrogen production heat circulation system and a hydrogen-rich blast furnace-converter system. Wherein the nuclear energy power generation system inputs electric energy and water vapor of Rankine cycle to the nuclear energy hydrogen production heat circulation system by utilizing heat energy of helium and electric energy generated by a steam turbine, the nuclear energy hydrogen production heat circulation system is subjected to a thermal chemical reaction to generate hydrogen and oxygen, and the hydrogen and the oxygen are heated and waste heat is collected under the action of the nuclear energy power generation system; and after entering a hydrogen-rich blast furnace-converter system, carrying out a reduction-oxidation reaction to produce steel, generating electric energy from oxidized slag through a Carrona cycle, supplying the electric energy to furnace top gas for cyclic collection and utilization, and circulating furnace top gas washing wastewater to a nuclear power generation system. According to the invention, gradient full utilization of energy is realized, the problems of hydrogen source and heating of the current hydrogen-rich blast furnace are solved, and the overall efficiency, safety and economical efficiency of the system can be improved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种核能发电、供热耦合富氢高炉‑转炉的综合循环系统，系统包括核能发电系统、核能制氢热循环系统、富氢高炉‑转炉系统。其中，核能发电系统通过利用氦气的热能和汽轮机产生的电能对核能制氢热循环系统输入电能和朗肯循环的水蒸汽，核能制氢热循环系统发生热化学反应生成氢气和氧气，分别在核能发电系统的作用下升温和收集余热，在进入富氢高炉‑转炉系统发生还原氧化反应生产钢，氧化的渣通过卡罗纳循环产生电能供给炉顶煤气循环收集利用，并将炉顶煤气洗涤废水循环至核能发电系统。本发明对能源实现分梯度的充分利用，解决目前富氢高炉的氢气来源和加热问题，可以提高系统整体效率、安全性和经济性。"
                }
            ]
